summary:
Every employer I have worked for has been heavily involved in computational engineering. My preference has always been Computational Fluid Dynamics (CFD) although one employer did deploy me on structural analysis, known as FEA for a few years. This employer taught me to construct hexahedral meshes for any geometry.

Specialties: Computational Fluid Dynamics - CFD
Hexahedral meshing
Fluent and Gambit
C / C++ & Fortran Programming
